WEBVTT

00:00:27.032 --> 00:00:30.035
What if what happened
last time happens again?

00:00:30.160 --> 00:00:32.162
I cannot promise you
it won't happen again.

00:00:32.412 --> 00:00:33.580
But I can promise you...

00:00:33.580 --> 00:00:35.707
that I will protect
you the best I can.

00:00:37.334 --> 00:00:40.253
I am giving you a lifetime
suspension, Ms."Sagwa."

00:00:40.253 --> 00:00:41.504
It's Sigua! You can't!

00:00:41.504 --> 00:00:43.340
Yes, I can!

00:00:44.716 --> 00:00:46.384
Why isn't it pink anymore?

00:00:46.468 --> 00:00:48.094
I threw out all of your trash.

00:00:48.386 --> 00:00:49.846
I did not agree to that.

00:00:50.305 --> 00:00:53.224
In fact, I don't like you
working with my wife.

00:00:53.224 --> 00:00:56.269
Well, your wife doesn't seem to
have a problem working with me.

00:00:56.519 --> 00:00:58.647
Dodong and I will help you sell.

00:01:09.157 --> 00:01:10.158
Don't get ahead of yourself.

00:01:10.158 --> 00:01:12.035
You might start
thinking that I'm thinking

00:01:12.035 --> 00:01:13.995
you're handsome even
when you're all sweaty.

00:01:14.329 --> 00:01:15.121
Okay.

00:01:15.121 --> 00:01:16.056
Hey, miss!

00:01:16.081 --> 00:01:17.307
My order.

00:01:17.332 --> 00:01:18.249
Wait, sis.

00:01:18.500 --> 00:01:20.960
I hope your power gets cut off.

00:01:22.504 --> 00:01:24.172
Oh, I know.

00:01:24.798 --> 00:01:27.050
I'll just text him the threats.

00:01:29.552 --> 00:01:31.513
I just need to speak
to Ezekiel first.

00:01:31.805 --> 00:01:32.739
Speak.

00:01:32.764 --> 00:01:33.698
In private.

00:01:33.723 --> 00:01:34.803
I hope.

00:01:38.728 --> 00:01:40.897
Then maybe she should
know you're a mafia boss.

00:01:41.356 --> 00:01:42.440
I won't say a word.

00:01:42.857 --> 00:01:44.943
But only if you do
something for me.

00:01:46.528 --> 00:01:47.585
Zeke?

00:01:48.363 --> 00:01:49.444
Shit.

00:01:50.030 --> 00:01:51.448
Ouch!

00:01:57.580 --> 00:01:59.416
Ezekiel is mine.

00:02:00.166 --> 00:02:01.501
Stupid girl.

00:02:01.626 --> 00:02:03.503
Are you really challenging me?

00:02:09.134 --> 00:02:09.926
Gosh.

00:02:09.926 --> 00:02:11.344
What's so funny?

00:02:11.720 --> 00:02:13.847
You're just such a stupid girl.

00:02:43.084 --> 00:02:44.878
Who are you calling a stupid girl?

00:02:52.135 --> 00:02:53.149
Aemie.

00:03:43.895 --> 00:03:44.813
What the heck?!

00:03:44.813 --> 00:03:46.142
Someone's taking a dump in here!

00:03:46.314 --> 00:03:47.649
Show some respect!

00:03:49.692 --> 00:03:51.027
I can't breathe!

00:03:56.991 --> 00:03:57.992
What did I do?

00:04:00.286 --> 00:04:02.831
Why didn't you tell
me I was choking her?

00:04:05.750 --> 00:04:06.626
Uh, sorry, sis.

00:04:07.585 --> 00:04:08.595
Come on.

00:04:09.128 --> 00:04:11.589
I was only trying to work. But
somehow, I get choked?

00:04:25.562 --> 00:04:26.563
Motherfucker!

00:04:26.563 --> 00:04:28.690
Can't even take a shit
in peace around here!

00:04:31.330 --> 00:04:32.095
What?

00:04:33.194 --> 00:04:34.112
What did she say?

00:04:47.125 --> 00:04:48.126
Ma'am Aemie?

00:04:51.504 --> 00:04:52.714
Are you okay, Ma'am Aemie?

00:04:53.172 --> 00:04:53.840
Uhh.

00:04:57.385 --> 00:04:59.554
Could you take me
to the university?

00:05:01.055 --> 00:05:02.223
Sure, let's go.

00:05:07.437 --> 00:05:08.271
What happened?

00:05:29.042 --> 00:05:30.335
Jacob, Sebastian.

00:05:31.669 --> 00:05:32.552
Ma'am Aemie.

00:05:34.380 --> 00:05:36.758
Have you known
Fiona for a long time?

00:05:39.169 --> 00:05:40.083
Lerwick.

00:05:41.888 --> 00:05:42.680
You answer.

00:05:43.014 --> 00:05:44.265
Why me? You do it.

00:05:44.974 --> 00:05:45.725
You answer.

00:05:47.977 --> 00:05:49.145
Uh, well.

00:05:50.605 --> 00:05:51.522
For a while.

00:05:51.522 --> 00:05:52.565
Why do you ask, Ma'am Aemie?

00:05:58.696 --> 00:05:59.822
Does Zeke love her?

00:06:15.129 --> 00:06:15.880
It's okay.

00:06:16.506 --> 00:06:17.548
You don't have to answer.

00:06:29.560 --> 00:06:30.603
Did something happen?

00:06:31.646 --> 00:06:32.605
I don't know either.

00:06:33.481 --> 00:06:34.816
But it's so unusual.

00:06:36.109 --> 00:06:38.194
It's so unusual to see
Ma'am Aemie like this.

00:06:39.529 --> 00:06:40.289
Let's go.

00:06:52.291 --> 00:06:53.459
Hey, Aemie girl.

00:06:54.043 --> 00:06:55.003
Are you okay?

00:06:55.670 --> 00:06:56.295
Sorry,

00:06:56.546 --> 00:06:58.131
my class just ran long.

00:06:59.007 --> 00:07:00.049
Have you been waiting here long?

00:07:03.219 --> 00:07:04.512
Fiona and Zeke...

00:07:05.346 --> 00:07:06.389
kissed.

00:07:07.146 --> 00:07:08.032
What?!

00:07:08.057 --> 00:07:10.727
You should have grabbed her hair
and slapped her as hard as you could!

00:07:12.103 --> 00:07:12.645
Oh no!

00:07:12.645 --> 00:07:14.147
Is that really what
you're supposed to do?

00:07:14.981 --> 00:07:15.523
Yes!

00:07:15.523 --> 00:07:16.816
I just left.

00:07:21.487 --> 00:07:23.573
Because at that
moment, I felt like...

00:07:26.451 --> 00:07:28.619
like someone had died.

00:07:29.454 --> 00:07:30.705
Why is that, Cai?

00:07:32.790 --> 00:07:33.666
Aemie girl.

00:07:34.667 --> 00:07:36.377
You're really so innocent.

00:07:37.336 --> 00:07:39.464
You see, that's a good sign.

00:07:40.381 --> 00:07:42.341
That means you're in love.

00:07:42.717 --> 00:07:45.219
Because when you're in love...

00:07:45.470 --> 00:07:48.473
you become more vulnerable
to all kinds of emotions.

00:07:48.765 --> 00:07:51.225
Like happiness, sadness,

00:07:51.809 --> 00:07:54.620
longing, frustration, anger...

00:07:54.645 --> 00:07:55.688
and even pain.

00:07:57.440 --> 00:07:58.816
That's the power of love.

00:08:01.277 --> 00:08:03.321
I was about to start singing.

00:08:03.321 --> 00:08:04.280
But I can't.

00:08:04.280 --> 00:08:06.407
We might get copyrighted.

00:08:08.701 --> 00:08:10.369
Got it, got it.

00:08:11.079 --> 00:08:12.747
You know, I think...

00:08:14.916 --> 00:08:16.417
I really am in love.

00:08:18.419 --> 00:08:19.604
See?

00:08:19.629 --> 00:08:21.214
But the thing is...

00:08:21.589 --> 00:08:24.342
Do you even know the
story behind that kiss?

00:08:24.759 --> 00:08:25.838
I mean...

00:08:26.511 --> 00:08:28.930
Have you and your husband
already talked about it?

00:08:33.142 --> 00:08:33.768
So...

00:08:35.144 --> 00:08:36.729
You don't have
to stress yourself.

00:08:37.271 --> 00:08:38.147
I mean...

00:08:38.147 --> 00:08:40.274
you're the wife and
he's your husband.

00:08:40.691 --> 00:08:41.818
You have every right.

00:08:44.862 --> 00:08:45.488
Exactly.

00:08:45.488 --> 00:08:46.697
To hell with that bitch.

00:08:46.989 --> 00:08:47.990
Exactly!

00:08:48.241 --> 00:08:49.784
You should've skinned her alive.

00:08:49.867 --> 00:08:50.868
Exactly!

00:08:50.868 --> 00:08:51.594
Hey!

00:08:51.619 --> 00:08:52.286
Oh my!

00:08:52.453 --> 00:08:54.539
- Hey, that's pretty morbid!
- I'm just kidding!

00:08:54.789 --> 00:08:56.416
Erase that, erase
that. Erase that.

00:08:58.918 --> 00:09:00.002
But...

00:09:03.673 --> 00:09:05.299
Admittedly, Cai...

00:09:08.511 --> 00:09:10.513
Part of me...

00:09:11.430 --> 00:09:12.598
wanted to do it.

00:09:14.434 --> 00:09:15.977
I wanted to kill her.

00:09:18.354 --> 00:09:20.189
The moment I saw them together.

00:09:25.695 --> 00:09:26.529
But...

00:09:27.321 --> 00:09:28.614
Of course, I can't.

00:09:29.740 --> 00:09:32.243
I don't want my emotions
to get the better of me.

00:09:32.827 --> 00:09:34.871
I may be dumb and slow...

00:09:34.871 --> 00:09:35.746
But...

00:09:36.789 --> 00:09:40.209
I'm not letting my actions be
overpowered by my emotions.

00:09:41.544 --> 00:09:42.879
That's why I just walked away.

00:09:42.879 --> 00:09:44.213
I didn't stay.

00:09:46.507 --> 00:09:47.717
You know...

00:09:48.676 --> 00:09:50.887
I hurt someone today.

00:09:50.887 --> 00:09:51.512
What?!

00:09:51.762 --> 00:09:52.697
Uh-huh.

00:09:52.722 --> 00:09:54.265
I choked her, Cai.

00:09:55.057 --> 00:09:55.933
- I choked her.
- You choked her?

00:09:55.933 --> 00:09:57.143
But I did apologize.

00:09:57.143 --> 00:09:59.187
I really didn't
mean to, I promise!

00:10:00.229 --> 00:10:01.564
I don't know.

00:10:01.564 --> 00:10:03.399
I think I'm going crazy.

00:10:04.483 --> 00:10:04.984
No.

00:10:05.151 --> 00:10:06.794
You're not crazy.

00:10:06.819 --> 00:10:08.182
It just runs in your blood.

00:10:08.988 --> 00:10:09.760
Huh?

00:10:10.948 --> 00:10:11.407
Huh?

00:10:11.407 --> 00:10:12.479
Nothing, nothing.

00:10:13.659 --> 00:10:14.927
Where's your ring?

00:10:14.952 --> 00:10:16.065
It's--

00:10:19.081 --> 00:10:20.041
Oh no.

00:10:20.750 --> 00:10:21.792
Oh no, Cai!

00:10:22.460 --> 00:10:23.711
Where's my ring?

00:10:27.757 --> 00:10:28.257
Oh no.

00:10:28.966 --> 00:10:30.885
Oh no, it's gone. Where is it?

00:10:42.396 --> 00:10:43.189
Zeke?

00:10:43.940 --> 00:10:45.036
Shit.

00:10:46.359 --> 00:10:48.819
- Please.
- Just let me go!

00:10:56.452 --> 00:10:57.286
Damn it!

00:11:04.585 --> 00:11:06.420
What the fuck are
you laughing at?

00:11:09.340 --> 00:11:10.591
Just relax, Mr. Roswell.

00:11:11.300 --> 00:11:11.968
What happened?

00:11:11.968 --> 00:11:13.135
Why are you so pissed?

00:11:16.222 --> 00:11:18.391
It's none of your
fucking damn business.

00:11:20.101 --> 00:11:21.018
Okay.

00:11:21.852 --> 00:11:22.645
Sorry.

00:11:24.313 --> 00:11:25.147
I'll get going.

00:11:26.774 --> 00:11:27.900
I'm leaving.

00:11:30.987 --> 00:11:31.904
I love her.

00:11:44.125 --> 00:11:45.459
She saw me with Fiona.

00:11:47.753 --> 00:11:48.754
But fuck!

00:11:49.505 --> 00:11:51.048
I never wanted to be kissed.

00:11:53.968 --> 00:11:55.594
I tried to talk to her but...

00:11:56.554 --> 00:11:58.306
I don't know what to fucking do.

00:12:00.099 --> 00:12:01.225
Just relax, Mr. Roswell.

00:12:01.475 --> 00:12:02.059
Breathe.

00:12:02.059 --> 00:12:02.601
Inhale.

00:12:04.353 --> 00:12:05.187
Exhale.

00:12:10.609 --> 00:12:11.277
Sorry.

00:12:12.320 --> 00:12:13.988
Did you try talking to Aemie?

00:12:14.739 --> 00:12:16.490
Are you fucking
nuts, Lamperouge?

00:12:17.491 --> 00:12:19.035
Do you think I didn't do that?

00:12:22.038 --> 00:12:22.830
I tried.

00:12:24.498 --> 00:12:25.207
But...

00:12:27.126 --> 00:12:29.337
But she just left
me dumbfounded.

00:12:33.591 --> 00:12:34.759
Don't get mad, Mr. Roswell.

00:12:34.759 --> 00:12:35.801
I have one more question.

00:12:38.137 --> 00:12:40.514
How many times have
you tried talking to Aemie?

00:13:29.105 --> 00:13:32.942
Why am I crying?

00:13:33.984 --> 00:13:37.113
Why am I so emotional?

00:13:47.841 --> 00:13:48.967
Go ahead!

00:13:49.291 --> 00:13:51.544
Just stab me with
this remote already!

00:13:51.544 --> 00:13:52.670
Go on!

00:13:57.758 --> 00:13:59.427
It hurts so much!

00:14:00.094 --> 00:14:02.388
It hurts so much!

00:14:02.888 --> 00:14:04.515
Crispin!

00:14:06.183 --> 00:14:07.351
Basilio!

00:14:07.768 --> 00:14:09.728
It hurts so much!

00:14:14.442 --> 00:14:16.944
It hurts so much!

00:14:23.075 --> 00:14:24.952
Oh my god!

00:14:26.996 --> 00:14:27.913
Could it be...

00:14:30.124 --> 00:14:31.500
that I'm pregnant?

00:14:46.765 --> 00:14:49.226
I think I'm pregnant!

00:14:49.810 --> 00:14:52.438
I think I'm pregnant!

00:15:48.452 --> 00:15:51.580
There's a Dollie
doll at Dollie Mart!

00:15:51.580 --> 00:15:53.123
They made it!

00:15:53.415 --> 00:15:55.626
I'm so happy!

00:16:09.723 --> 00:16:10.474
Fuck!

00:16:13.185 --> 00:16:14.687
I need to fix this.

00:16:47.803 --> 00:16:49.263
It hurts so much.

00:17:42.191 --> 00:17:44.443
Why did it have
to end up like that?

00:17:57.706 --> 00:17:58.916
I'm sorry, wife.

00:17:59.458 --> 00:18:00.584
I never meant to.

00:18:00.834 --> 00:18:01.543
Look,

00:18:01.919 --> 00:18:03.879
she initiated the kiss.

00:18:04.505 --> 00:18:05.965
I don't love her anymore.

00:18:06.757 --> 00:18:08.175
Wife, please believe me.

00:18:08.759 --> 00:18:10.177
I love you and...

00:18:16.517 --> 00:18:17.518
Who are you talking to?

00:18:21.313 --> 00:18:22.773
I was just trying to...

00:18:24.983 --> 00:18:25.609
What?

00:18:30.030 --> 00:18:31.615
I was just trying to call you.

00:18:32.241 --> 00:18:33.492
I cooked dinner.

00:18:40.165 --> 00:18:41.542
Come on, let's go downstairs.

00:19:05.733 --> 00:19:07.317
What happened to Zeke?

00:19:10.154 --> 00:19:11.655
That's between him and Fiona.

00:20:43.121 --> 00:20:44.042
Come on,

00:20:45.123 --> 00:20:46.144
let's eat.

00:20:49.044 --> 00:20:50.011
Uhh.

00:20:51.964 --> 00:20:53.507
I was just going to drink some water.

00:20:57.427 --> 00:20:58.846
Don't you like the food?

00:21:04.810 --> 00:21:06.228
Because, Zeke...

00:21:06.520 --> 00:21:07.441
It's okay.

00:21:07.688 --> 00:21:09.064
I'll make something else.

00:21:11.608 --> 00:21:13.068
What do you prefer to eat?

00:21:17.906 --> 00:21:19.491
I'm not hungry.

00:21:19.491 --> 00:21:20.742
And I need to leave too.

00:21:28.876 --> 00:21:30.168
Where are you going?

00:21:35.195 --> 00:21:38.490
I'm really starving.

00:21:38.719 --> 00:21:41.805
I've been wanting
to eat for a while now.

00:21:42.347 --> 00:21:47.060
But I'm worried Zeke will
notice I'm not wearing my ring.

00:21:48.353 --> 00:21:51.982
So I texted Caileigh to
come with me to buy a ring.

00:21:53.233 --> 00:21:54.735
I'll eat later.

00:21:56.653 --> 00:21:57.654
I'm asking you,

00:21:59.031 --> 00:22:00.073
where are you going?

00:22:02.534 --> 00:22:05.704
Caileigh and I are just
meeting up because

00:22:06.747 --> 00:22:09.041
it's been a while
since we last bonded.

00:22:09.833 --> 00:22:10.709
Bonding?

00:22:11.460 --> 00:22:12.363
At this hour?

00:22:13.879 --> 00:22:15.797
No, you're staying here.

00:22:15.797 --> 00:22:16.548
It's safer.

00:22:18.091 --> 00:22:19.843
- Come on, Zeke...
- I said no!

00:22:21.929 --> 00:22:23.013
And that's final.

00:22:27.225 --> 00:22:29.019
Why do you always
have to get your way?

00:22:30.562 --> 00:22:32.314
Zeke, I'm not a kid anymore.

00:22:33.148 --> 00:22:34.900
Caileigh and I are
just meeting up.

00:22:36.151 --> 00:22:39.613
Why won't you give me
the right to do what I want?

00:22:47.246 --> 00:22:48.152
I'm sorry.

00:22:52.668 --> 00:22:55.504
Even though I'm really starving.

00:23:27.494 --> 00:23:30.288
I'm really sorry, Cai.
I'm just so hungry.

00:23:30.288 --> 00:23:31.415
It's okay, girl.

00:23:32.332 --> 00:23:35.043
Did you find one that's
close to your ring?

00:23:36.586 --> 00:23:38.130
How about this one, ma'am?

00:23:41.091 --> 00:23:44.219
It doesn't really look like it, miss.

00:23:45.262 --> 00:23:46.680
No, not that one.

00:23:49.307 --> 00:23:50.684
Take a look at this one, girl.

00:23:51.435 --> 00:23:52.277
This one.

00:23:53.979 --> 00:23:55.188
It's pretty close.

00:23:56.606 --> 00:23:57.858
It kind of...

00:23:58.608 --> 00:23:59.443
looks like it.

00:23:59.818 --> 00:24:00.694
Are you sure?

00:24:01.153 --> 00:24:03.322
Cause I'm gonna
buy this one if it is.

00:24:05.449 --> 00:24:06.324
Oh, no. Wait, wait.

00:24:06.324 --> 00:24:07.034
No, not this one.

00:24:07.034 --> 00:24:09.995
Let's keep looking for
one that's even closer.

00:24:10.579 --> 00:24:11.449
Okay.

00:24:21.256 --> 00:24:22.466
Hello.

00:24:22.632 --> 00:24:25.010
Hello, ma'am/sir.
Congratulations.

00:24:25.010 --> 00:24:29.306
You just won a sports
car and 1 million pesos.

00:24:29.473 --> 00:24:30.974
In order to claim it,

00:24:31.266 --> 00:24:34.936
just give me the number on
the back of your credit card.

00:24:36.646 --> 00:24:39.149
This is legit. Seriously.

00:24:39.524 --> 00:24:40.317
Seriously?

00:24:40.567 --> 00:24:42.611
You can't fool me, scammer!

00:24:50.594 --> 00:24:52.596
I'm tired of dancing.

00:24:52.621 --> 00:24:54.206
Enough already, please.

00:24:54.623 --> 00:24:56.416
How many episodes
has it been now?

00:24:59.169 --> 00:25:00.962
Why are you so persistent, huh?

00:25:00.962 --> 00:25:02.172
You've been at it forever!

00:25:02.172 --> 00:25:04.466
How is the Yaji's heiress?

00:25:04.758 --> 00:25:07.594
Oh, sorry. Wrong number.

00:25:09.096 --> 00:25:10.555
Aemie Roswell.

00:25:11.473 --> 00:25:12.253
Yes?

00:25:12.790 --> 00:25:13.816
Wanna play?

00:25:16.186 --> 00:25:17.104
Play?

00:25:17.312 --> 00:25:18.980
Oh! Over the phone?

00:25:19.689 --> 00:25:20.315
Oh, I can't.

00:25:20.315 --> 00:25:22.109
Let's do it tomorrow.
It's already late.

00:25:22.484 --> 00:25:23.777
Or just come over to our house.

00:25:23.777 --> 00:25:25.362
I still have an extra
dollhouse there.

00:25:26.738 --> 00:25:28.198
We'll meet soon, my dear.

00:25:28.198 --> 00:25:29.157
Very soon.

00:25:29.157 --> 00:25:29.950
Okay then.

00:25:29.950 --> 00:25:30.826
Bye-bye!

