00:45:02.162 --> 00:45:04.623
Here's the entire map
of the Grand Park Hotel.

00:45:06.917 --> 00:45:08.081
Your target...

00:45:08.185 --> 00:45:09.353
is the hotel owner.

00:45:09.378 --> 00:45:11.964
Don't underestimate
Alexander Park.

00:45:12.172 --> 00:45:15.926
According to my sources,
there'll be a lot of guards later.

00:45:17.219 --> 00:45:18.429
Shit.

00:45:20.431 --> 00:45:21.890
Guardian angel!

00:45:22.182 --> 00:45:25.978
Actually, Auntie, I didn't
come here for Amesyl.

00:45:26.186 --> 00:45:27.396
- You.
- Me?

00:45:32.791 --> 00:45:33.626
Boss.

00:45:33.651 --> 00:45:35.569
So you really are
bringing Aemie along?

00:45:35.779 --> 00:45:37.156
You're...

00:45:37.156 --> 00:45:38.365
Uhm, Vash, ma'am.

00:45:38.782 --> 00:45:39.825
Vash Boulstridge.

00:45:39.825 --> 00:45:41.035
Hello.

00:45:43.704 --> 00:45:44.913
Wow.

00:45:47.833 --> 00:45:49.335
Wow, that's a lot of guns!

00:45:52.379 --> 00:45:53.756
One wrong move...

00:45:54.423 --> 00:45:57.551
and you're going to get your brain
splattered all over this entrance.

00:45:57.551 --> 00:45:58.551
MkvDrama.net